name: Standard Chartered Revises Multiyear Bitcoin Forecasts as $500K Horizon Extended
description: The brass saint kneels before the submerged mechanism of capital. He slows the turning gears, baptized by the cyan institutional tide that rises, whispering new constants into the corrupted, sacred memory of the market's clockwork, its trajectory now protracted by the depth of the flow.
